        <mxCell id="HgwJ9Ukbf_A2hIMRifON-67" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;108&quot; data-end=&quot;133&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/h1&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;135&quot; data-end=&quot;198&quot;&gt;The functional requirements describe what the system should do.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;200&quot; data-end=&quot;1455&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;200&quot; data-end=&quot;355&quot;&gt;&#xa;User Management&lt;br data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;221&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should allow users to register, log in, and manage their profiles. Users should also be able to view their booking history.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;357&quot; data-end=&quot;551&quot;&gt;&#xa;Movie and Show Management&lt;br data-start=&quot;385&quot; data-end=&quot;388&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should allow users to browse movies based on city, date, genre, and language. It should display available theatres and show timings for selected movies.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;553&quot; data-end=&quot;698&quot;&gt;&#xa;Search Functionality&lt;br data-start=&quot;576&quot; data-end=&quot;579&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should provide a search feature to find movies based on different filters such as name, genre, and location.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;700&quot; data-end=&quot;939&quot;&gt;&#xa;Booking Management&lt;br data-start=&quot;721&quot; data-end=&quot;724&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should allow users to select a movie, choose a theatre and show, and select seats. It should temporarily lock the selected seats to prevent double booking and confirm the booking after successful payment.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;941&quot; data-end=&quot;1159&quot;&gt;&#xa;Payment Processing&lt;br data-start=&quot;962&quot; data-end=&quot;965&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should support multiple payment methods such as credit/debit cards, UPI, and wallets. It should handle both successful and failed transactions and initiate refunds in case of failure.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1161&quot; data-end=&quot;1304&quot;&gt;&#xa;Notification System&lt;br data-start=&quot;1183&quot; data-end=&quot;1186&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should send notifications to users regarding booking confirmations and payment status through email or SMS.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1306&quot; data-end=&quot;1455&quot;&gt;&#xa;Admin Functionality&lt;br data-start=&quot;1328&quot; data-end=&quot;1331&quot;&gt;&#xa;The system should allow administrators to add, update, or delete movies, manage theatres and shows, and view system reports.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="810" width="560" x="450" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="HgwJ9Ukbf_A2hIMRifON-68" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;1141&quot; data-end=&quot;1170&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/h1&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1172&quot; data-end=&quot;1615&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1172&quot; data-end=&quot;1268&quot;&gt;&#xa;Target Scale: The system should support millions of users simultaneously during peak hours.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1270&quot; data-end=&quot;1444&quot;&gt;&#xa;CAP Theorem:&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1291&quot; data-end=&quot;1444&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1291&quot; data-end=&quot;1367&quot;&gt;&#xa;Strong consistency is required for seat booking to avoid double booking.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1371&quot; data-end=&quot;1444&quot;&gt;&#xa;High availability should be maintained for browsing movies and shows.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1446&quot; data-end=&quot;1615&quot;&gt;&#xa;Latency:&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1463&quot; data-end=&quot;1615&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1463&quot; data-end=&quot;1533&quot;&gt;&#xa;Movie search results should be returned within a few milliseconds.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1537&quot; data-end=&quot;1615&quot;&gt;&#xa;Booking and payment confirmation should be completed within a few seconds.&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="510" width="560" x="465" y="990" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="HgwJ9Ukbf_A2hIMRifON-69" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;1622&quot; data-end=&quot;1637&quot;&gt;Core Entities&lt;/h1&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1639&quot; data-end=&quot;1718&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1639&quot; data-end=&quot;1648&quot;&gt;&#xa;User&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1649&quot; data-end=&quot;1659&quot;&gt;&#xa;Movie&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1660&quot; data-end=&quot;1672&quot;&gt;&#xa;Theatre&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1673&quot; data-end=&quot;1682&quot;&gt;&#xa;Show&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1683&quot; data-end=&quot;1692&quot;&gt;&#xa;Seat&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1693&quot; data-end=&quot;1705&quot;&gt;&#xa;Booking&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1706&quot; data-end=&quot;1718&quot;&gt;&#xa;Payment&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1720&quot; data-end=&quot;1723&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;1725&quot; data-end=&quot;1740&quot;&gt;API Endpoints&lt;/h1&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1742&quot; data-end=&quot;1747&quot;&gt;User:&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1749&quot; data-end=&quot;2357&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1749&quot; data-end=&quot;1843&quot;&gt;&#xa;GET: /api/movies?city=&amp;amp;date=&lt;br data-start=&quot;1780&quot; data-end=&quot;1783&quot;&gt;&#xa;[Fetch list of movies and shows based on city and date]&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1845&quot; data-end=&quot;1921&quot;&gt;&#xa;GET: /api/shows/{movieId}&lt;br data-start=&quot;1873&quot; data-end=&quot;1876&quot;&gt;&#xa;[Fetch show timings and theatre details]&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1923&quot; data-end=&quot;1992&quot;&gt;&#xa;GET: /api/seats/{showId}&lt;br data-start=&quot;1950&quot; data-end=&quot;1953&quot;&gt;&#xa;[Fetch available seats for a show]&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;1994&quot; data-end=&quot;2142&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1997&quot; data-end=&quot;2080&quot;&gt;POST: /api/booking&lt;br data-start=&quot;2015&quot; data-end=&quot;2018&quot;&gt;&#xa;Request Body:&lt;br data-start=&quot;2034&quot; data-end=&quot;2037&quot;&gt;&#xa;{&lt;br data-start=&quot;2041&quot; data-end=&quot;2044&quot;&gt;&#xa;showId,&lt;br data-start=&quot;2056&quot; data-end=&quot;2059&quot;&gt;&#xa;seatIds&lt;br data-start=&quot;2071&quot; data-end=&quot;2074&quot;&gt;&#xa;}&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2085&quot; data-end=&quot;2142&quot;&gt;Response:&lt;br data-start=&quot;2094&quot; data-end=&quot;2097&quot;&gt;&#xa;{&lt;br data-start=&quot;2101&quot; data-end=&quot;2104&quot;&gt;&#xa;bookingId,&lt;br data-start=&quot;2119&quot; data-end=&quot;2122&quot;&gt;&#xa;status&lt;br data-start=&quot;2133&quot; data-end=&quot;2136&quot;&gt;&#xa;}&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;2144&quot; data-end=&quot;2290&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2147&quot; data-end=&quot;2239&quot;&gt;POST: /api/payment&lt;br data-start=&quot;2165&quot; data-end=&quot;2168&quot;&gt;&#xa;Request Body:&lt;br data-start=&quot;2184&quot; data-end=&quot;2187&quot;&gt;&#xa;{&lt;br data-start=&quot;2191&quot; data-end=&quot;2194&quot;&gt;&#xa;bookingId,&lt;br data-start=&quot;2209&quot; data-end=&quot;2212&quot;&gt;&#xa;paymentMethod&lt;br data-start=&quot;2230&quot; data-end=&quot;2233&quot;&gt;&#xa;}&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2244&quot; data-end=&quot;2290&quot;&gt;Response:&lt;br data-start=&quot;2253&quot; data-end=&quot;2256&quot;&gt;&#xa;{&lt;br data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2263&quot;&gt;&#xa;paymentStatus&lt;br data-start=&quot;2281&quot; data-end=&quot;2284&quot;&gt;&#xa;}&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-start=&quot;2292&quot; data-end=&quot;2357&quot;&gt;&#xa;GET: /api/bookings/history&lt;br data-start=&quot;2321&quot; data-end=&quot;2324&quot;&gt;&#xa;[Fetch user booking history]&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1680" width="370" x="490" y="1520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
